'''Françoise Ellong''' (wavutse 8 Gashyantare 1988) ni umuyobozi wa firime n'umwanditsi wa filimi muri [[Kameruni]].

== Ubuzima ==
Ellong yavukiye Douala, muri [[Kameruni]] mu 1988. Afite imyaka 11, yimukiye i Brunoy kubana na nyirarume, maze yandika inkuru ye ya mbere. Ellong yitabiriye amarushanwa y'abanditsi bato bavuga [[igifaransa]] mu 2002. Kubera amarushanwa, yagize ubushake bwo kwandika amashusho. 

Mu 2006, filime ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Les Colocs'', yarasohotse. Ellong yayoboye filime ye ya mbere yerekana, ''WAKA'', mu 2013. yanditswe na Séraphin Kakouang, bishingiye ku nkuru y'umwimerere ya Ellong. ''WAKA'' yahawe igihembo cyihariye cy’abacamanza mu iserukiramuco du Cinéma Africain de Khouribga, ndetse n’igihembo cya Dikalo mu iserukiramuco rya Pan-African Cannes.  Yerekanwe mugutangira ibirori bya Ecrans Noirs. Filime ye ya kabiri yerekana, ''Buried'', yasohotse muri 2020. Nibijyanye no guhura kwinshuti zo mu bwana numukino wagaragaje amabanga.  Ifata amashusho mu mudugudu wa Nkassomo, yatewe inkunga na raporo yamakuru yabonye kuri tereviziyo. 

Usibye kwandika no kuyobora, Ellong yasohoye igitabo "Journal Intime d'Un Meurtrier" mu 2008.  Muri 2016, yatangije blog "Le Film Camerounais", bituma ibihembo bya LFC.  Ellong yasabye ko hajyaho inkambi z’abakinnyi ba Thierry Ntamack mu 2020, Ntamack amaze kuvuga ko 10 ku ijana gusa by’abakinnyi ba [[Kameruni]] ari beza. 

